<i>adverb</i>: 원만히 [원만히], 순순히 [순순히], 나긋나긋 [나근나귿], 그윽이 [그으기] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>원만히 [원만히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mildly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 부드럽고 너그럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's personality being gentle and generous.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smoothly; peacefully</dd><br>
<dd>일의 진행이 순조롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the progress of something is smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. intimately; harmoniously</dd><br>
<dd>서로 사이가 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of getting along well with each other.</dd><br>
<dt>순순히 [순순히]</dt><br>
<dd>mildly</dd><br>
<dd>타이르는 태도가 아주 다정하고 친절하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one is very kind and tender when scolding someone.</dd><br>
<dt>나긋나긋 [나근나귿]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부로 전해지는 느낌이 매우 연하고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling soft and mild on the skin.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mildly; amiably</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 태도가 매우 상냥하고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a very kind and soft personality or attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>그윽이 [그으기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietly; intimately</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 주는 느낌이 깊고 평안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of giving deep and peaceful feelings.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gently; mildly</dd><br>
<dd>인상이나 느낌이 은근하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of looking or feeling soft.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>